ED_Title: Effective date of resolutions relating to the peacekeeping budget and special political missions
ED_DecisionText: At its 97th plenary meeting, on 3 July 2019, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Fifth Committee (A/73/936, para. 11),  decided that all resolutions relating to the peacekeeping budget and special political missions adopted at its 97th meeting, on 3 July 2019, under agenda items 136, 150 to 155 and 157 to 166, would be effective as from 1 July 2019.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of this decision will be contained in the official record of the GA (A/73/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
